Key Match Events: Orlando Arcia hit two home runs in the game
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was a continuation of a subplot that began during last year's postseason between Orlando Arcia and Bryce Harper
Others: The Braves have won 13 of 18 since blowing an 8-2 eighth-inning lead against the Rockies at Coors Field on Aug. 11. They also have won eight of 11 since learning on Aug. 19 that Austin Riley will miss the remainder of the regular season with a broken hand.
